data.description:
Beautiful townhome located in the gated 56 unit intracoastal community of Ocean Cay. This 3 bedroom 2 1/2 bath home is ideal for those who work at home with a private den/office located on the first floor. Second floor features a half bath, huge family room, oversized open kitchen with newer upgraded appliances, a large island and an even bigger breakfast bar. Kitchen Aid range with microwave/convection oven combo is ideal for those who love to cook and desire double ovens.All three bedrooms are located on the third floor along with 2 full baths. The spacious 2 car garage features a large storage closet and a Level 2 electric vehicle charger included. Impact glass on all windows for added security and storm protection. Smart thermostat, electronic locks, garage door and overhead lighting controlled via app or though Apple HomeKit.

Ocean Cay features a community pool plus private beach along the intracoastal where you can launch kayaks and watercraft or relax under the pergola while watching the boats pass by.

There is plenty of room for dogs in the fenced front yard or at the community dog run behind the pool. While Ocean Cay is a dog friendly community aggressive breeds are restricted but no weight limits apply.

AC replaced in 2019. Water heater replaced in 2022. Roof recently inspected.

*Onsite overnight street parking is only available to visitors/guests.
